💻 Terminal / User Flow

# Borrower Side
$ git clone https://github.com/<your-repo>
$ cd FinRisk
$ python app.py
> Access via http://localhost:5000

[Landing Page] --> Register/Login --> Dashboard
--> Enter Income & Expenses --> Loan Eligibility Checker
--> Apply Loan --> Track Status & Receive Notifications
--> View Analytics & Financial Advisory
--> Access Government Schemes / Courses

# Banker Side
Login --> View Unassigned Requests --> Pick Loan --> Approve / Reject / Manual Review
--> Performance Dashboard Updates in Real-time

# Admin Side
Login --> View Banks, Borrowers, and Loan Applications
--> Visualize Charts, Live System Stats
